variables.value: Oh? You all here for a football battle\nwith my kids?
Aw, you're no fun! Come back anytime.
Time to build that\nstamina. Let's go!
Gotta give it my all\nnext match...
Hey, I think I'm\ntougher than before!
Full of energy!\nLove to see it.
Had my days like that\ntoo... way back when.
Whoa! Right up the\nnose, that one.
The sea, some booze,\nand loud kids...
Don't let the heat get\nto you.
Keep up the trainin'.\nYou're killing it!
Caught the news too.\nCan't miss it!
Ew,\nthis is a pain to eat!
